Reasoning: The paper deals with face recognition, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). It also involves evaluating different algorithms for assessing similarity, which falls under machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of the labeled faces in the wild (LFW) dataset suggests a focus on multimedia (cs.MM). Finally, the paper also addresses the issue of rejecting/ignoring unknown identities, which relates to computer security (cs.CR).
